<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_439_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / von ewrs Suns wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l4">vnd des dem das awg <expan>awſgeſtoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daran hab </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_439_r1l3">daʒ </ab></add> ewr Sun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l5">daran nicht ſchulde rat vnd tat hab vnd das wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l6">werd / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Nu ıſt ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l7">Sun <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> vaſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lewmunt</expan> / wil er ſich aber des vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Rate <expan>verantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / . Darcʒü <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jm vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_r1l9">geleitt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> k </del> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>hiecʒwich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant Görgen tag ſchirſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_439_line_1576423321651_3852">wenn er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_439_line_1576423385753_3895">nach den </ab><ab facs="#facs_439_line_1576423392675_3900"><expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>veirtage<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒü vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> fi </del> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
