<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad,</ex></expan> als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von ewrs suns
                        wegen und des, dem das awg <expan>awsgestoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist,
                            <add>daz</add> ewr sun daran nicht schulde rat und tat hab und das wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan> werd,
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stande<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu ist ewr sun
                                <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> vast
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lewmunt,</expan> wil er sich aber des vor
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate
                            <expan>verantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, darczü
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im unser geleitt
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hieczwich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant Görgen tag schirst</q>23.04.1412</note></app>, wenn er
                            <add>nach den <expan>ost<ex>er</ex>veirtage<ex>n</ex></expan></add> czü
                        uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
